// CollapsibleSection
// Generic collapsible panel with a labeled header and toggle chevron.
// Used throughout the design editor's properties/layers panels to group
// related controls.

FUNCTION CollapsibleSection(title, children, defaultOpen, className) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Tracks isOpen state. Renders a clickable header row (title + chevron).
  Chevron rotates 180° when open. Body content shown only when open.
